kout and get Free Delivery to the following Airports:<\/p><ul><li>Los Angeles (LAX)<\/li><\/ul><p>We provide food, water, and comfort for your kitten's journey - we care about our babies!<\/p><p>We will book the flight and give you all needed information to pick up your kitten. You have to show your ID and number of AWB at the airline’s facility.<br\/><br\/>Please see our <a href=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shipping Policy\">shipping policy<\/a> for more information.<\/p>"}},"2bc4c687-6a03-4f15-9a88-cd136f5377b5":{"type":"tab_content","settings":{"question":"Delivery by Plane in Cargo","text":"<p>For delivery to any airports not listed above, the shipping price is $580. <\/p><p>We provide food, water, and comfort for your kitten's journey - we care about our babies!<\/p><p>We book the flight and give you all needed information to pick up your kitten. You will have to show your ID and number of AWB at the airline’s facility.<\/p><p>Please see our <a href=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shipping Policy\">shipping policy<\/a> for more information.<\/p>"}},"0fc4c86d-7ebb-4c1e-b433-c2c4790fb960":{"type":"tab_content","settings":{"question":"Nanny delivery","text":"<p>With a Nanny Delivery, our courier is flying together with your kitten, and sits with them for the whole flight. Price is $970 (exclusions may apply -depending on the destination). <\/p><p>We'll book the flight and give you all needed information to pick up your kitten.<\/p><p>Please see our <a href=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shipping Policy\">shipping policy<\/a> for more information.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--18133651751233__9d0a451f-e335-4545-a163-d1375a61dabd-1682272135ea40f628-0","2bc4c687-6a03-4f15-9a88-cd136f5377b5","0fc4c86d-7ebb-4c1e-b433-c2c4790fb960"],"settings":{"colors":"white","title":"Our Delivery Options","faq_icon":"caret"}},"7a2062a2-3d13-4fc8-bda6-16729af2c1be":{"type":"text--rich-text","setting